com.extensia.xcp.services.restapi.model.parameters.validators

Class MinMaxValidator

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.extensia.xcp.services.restapi.model.parameters.validators.MinMaxValidator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IntegerParameterValidator, TextParameterValidator

    public class MinMaxValidator
extends java.lang.Object
implements IntegerParameterValidator, TextParameterValidator
    Validator implementation class that performs min-max range checking for Image, Integer and Text parameters types. A separate validation method is provided for each of the supported request parameter types in order to support the corresponding validator interfaces.

    Note: The validator does not currently support a min or max value of -1 since that value is used as a special indicator to disable the max and/or min limit(s). This may change in a future version if this limitation becomes problematic.
